

Layer 0:
  Includes everything that can be computed without state or user interaction
  The code itself
  Includes all literal values
  Includes all expressions and function definitions
  Constant-folded values can be part of this layer

Layer 1:
  Includes user input
  Includes pseudorandom values
  Includes state based on layer 0

Layer N:
  Includes state based on layer N - 1
